{"tid":573982,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"hottoys或其他1/6 1/4 品牌 figures 討論區 7 派到佛誕都重係首日","createTime":"2018-02-27T03:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T17:20:58.000Z","uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff1f0b7047852e7f7c05495331e99954d7133bf","tid":573982,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"hottoys或其他1/6 1/4 品牌 figures 討論區 7 派到佛誕都重係首日<br />\n<br />\nHOT TOYS是一家源於香港的人偶的公司，專門向世界的市場開發、設計和出品大小1/6（約30公分高）及1/4(約45公分)的高精細度收藏性的可動關節的人偶，以像真人的頭雕、做工精巧細緻而出名。hot toy 公司成立於2000年，剛開始專門生產1:6比例的美軍特種部隊人物可動人偶，之後到現在以生產電影人物、電玩遊戲人物為主，尤其是他們的電影名作系列品牌（Movie Masterpiece Series）高端人偶。他們主要由畫家JC Hong所領導。和 yulli 頭雕師等人<br />\n<br />\nhottoys 電話37223988，有任何關於hottoys figures收訂/價錢查詢都可以打過去"},{"pid":"5a17dc259630319690d36025d173bb63b79e3993","tid":573982,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"如enterbay overtoys 或者其他廠既1/6 1/4 figure都可以入黎討論"},{"pid":"cd9c5a4e4100fdd97f8bf0eb5ad9de5ffdb53800","tid":573982,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/113933_94b9f48a92f8ceffe4f08acc123787e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F113933_94b9f48a92f8ceffe4f08acc123787e0.png&h=a0a0607b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/113934_046d877262590de5ef9fb7ed632761b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F113934_046d877262590de5ef9fb7ed632761b1.png&h=68eaa831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/113935_2864d137e09529d7fed382ec8261f381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F113935_2864d137e09529d7fed382ec8261f381.png&h